  "body": "## Description\r\n### Actual Behaviour\r\nDuplicated IBFT2 messages are not discarded when counting the Prepare messages included in a Prepared Certificate\r\n\r\n### Expected behaviour:** \r\nEither\r\n- Duplicated Prepare messages are discarded when counting the Prepare messages included in a Prepared Certificate\r\n- Message senders are counted and duplicated senders are discarded\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nThis bug was discovered as part of the formal specification and verification of an alternative BFT consensus protocol based on IBFT2.\r\n",
